snippet.title: MOUSE | Spike-D Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
Nothing says YOU more than a can of healthy spinach!

The latest gameplay teaser for MOUSE is here - featuring a first look at the game's Grappling Hook, Helicopter, and PowerUp Spinach in action!

Coming 2025. 
Wishlist on Steam now: https://bit.ly/MOUSESteam

Make sure you join our official Discord to stay up to date - https://discord.com/invite/tbYfWm6YCs
